name: Happenstance | PK-01
description:
A lone lantern occupies the cramped booth at the Hap Ryder Riverfront Theatre in Fairbanks, Alaska. As the house fills, other actors recite their lines for one last time. But your eyes, your eyes are fixated on that lantern..

The theatre was where I began founding my 'Ohana and this light was a close friend of mine throughout 2016 and 2017. Looking to it centered me and I'll forever be grateful for that community. As such, it seems fitting for it to start my Pre-K [PK] series with "Happenstance"
